{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Back in New York, I am the head of development"},{"time":2000,"text":"for a non-profit called Robin Hood."},{"time":5000,"text":"When I'm not fighting poverty, I'm fighting fires"},{"time":7000,"text":"as the assistant captain of a volunteer fire company."},{"time":10000,"text":"Now in our town,"},{"time":12000,"text":"where the volunteers supplement a highly skilled career staff,"},{"time":15000,"text":"you have to get to the fire scene pretty early"},{"time":17000,"text":"to get in on any action."}]},{"cues":[{"time":19000,"text":"I remember my first fire."},{"time":21000,"text":"I was the second volunteer on the scene,"},{"time":23000,"text":"so there was a pretty good chance I was going to get in."},{"time":26000,"text":"But still it was a real footrace against the other volunteers"},{"time":28000,"text":"to get to the captain in charge"},{"time":30000,"text":"to find out what our assignments would be."},{"time":32000,"text":"When I found the captain,"},{"time":34000,"text":"he was having a very engaging conversation"},{"time":36000,"text":"with the homeowner,"},{"time":38000,"text":"who was surely having one of the worst days of her life."},{"time":42000,"text":"Here it was, the middle of the night,"},{"time":44000,"text":"she was standing outside in the pouring rain,"},{"time":47000,"text":"under an umbrella, in her pajamas, barefoot,"},{"time":50000,"text":"while her house was in flames."}]},{"cues":[{"time":53000,"text":"The other volunteer who had arrived just before me --"},{"time":55000,"text":"let's call him Lex Luther --"},{"time":58000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":60000,"text":"got to the captain first"},{"time":62000,"text":"and was asked to go inside"},{"time":65000,"text":"and save the homeowner's dog."},{"time":68000,"text":"The dog! I was stunned with jealousy."},{"time":71000,"text":"Here was some lawyer or money manager"},{"time":73000,"text":"who, for the rest of his life, gets to tell people"},{"time":75000,"text":"that he went into a burning building"},{"time":77000,"text":"to save a living creature,"},{"time":79000,"text":"just because he beat me by five seconds."},{"time":82000,"text":"Well, I was next."},{"time":84000,"text":"The captain waved me over."},{"time":86000,"text":"He said, \"Bezos, I need you to go into the house."},{"time":89000,"text":"I need you to go upstairs, past the fire,"},{"time":92000,"text":"and I need you to get this woman a pair of shoes.\""},{"time":95000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":98000,"text":"I swear."},{"time":100000,"text":"So, not exactly what I was hoping for,"},{"time":103000,"text":"but off I went --"},{"time":105000,"text":"up the stairs, down the hall, past the 'real' firefighters,"},{"time":108000,"text":"who were pretty much done putting out the fire at this point,"},{"time":111000,"text":"into the master bedroom to get a pair of shoes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":114000,"text":"Now I know what you're thinking,"},{"time":117000,"text":"but I'm no hero."},{"time":119000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":124000,"text":"I carried my payload back downstairs"},{"time":127000,"text":"where I met my nemesis"},{"time":129000,"text":"and the precious dog by the front door."},{"time":131000,"text":"We took our treasures outside to the homeowner,"},{"time":134000,"text":"where, not surprisingly,"},{"time":136000,"text":"his received much more attention than did mine."},{"time":139000,"text":"A few weeks later,"},{"time":141000,"text":"the department received a letter from the homeowner"},{"time":143000,"text":"thanking us for the valiant effort displayed"},{"time":145000,"text":"in saving her home."},{"time":147000,"text":"The act of kindness she noted above all others:"},{"time":150000,"text":"someone had even gotten her a pair of shoes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":155000,"text":"In both my vocation at Robin Hood"},{"time":157000,"text":"and my avocation as a volunteer firefighter,"},{"time":159000,"text":"I am witness to acts of generosity and kindness"},{"time":162000,"text":"on a monumental scale,"},{"time":164000,"text":"but I'm also witness to acts of grace and courage"},{"time":166000,"text":"on an individual basis."},{"time":168000,"text":"And you know what I've learned?"},{"time":170000,"text":"They all matter."},{"time":172000,"text":"So as I look around this room"},{"time":174000,"text":"at people who either have achieved,"},{"time":176000,"text":"or are on their way to achieving,"},{"time":178000,"text":"remarkable levels of success,"},{"time":180000,"text":"I would offer this reminder:"},{"time":182000,"text":"don't wait."},{"time":184000,"text":"Don't wait until you make your first million"},{"time":186000,"text":"to make a difference in somebody's life."},{"time":188000,"text":"If you have something to give,"},{"time":190000,"text":"give it now."},{"time":192000,"text":"Serve food at a soup kitchen. Clean up a neighborhood park."},{"time":195000,"text":"Be a mentor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":197000,"text":"Not every day is going to offer us a chance"},{"time":199000,"text":"to save somebody's life,"},{"time":201000,"text":"but every day offers us an opportunity to affect one."},{"time":204000,"text":"So get in the game. Save the shoes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":207000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":209000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":214000,"text":"Bruno Giussani: Mark, Mark, come back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":216000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":223000,"text":"Mark Bezos: Thank you."}]}]}